{"h0e5ee6aag2347g4ae7g88f6g7db3a4d25e52": ["*The corpse seems willing to speak - but not to its killer.*", "NARRATOR", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Forest\\FOR_Bugbear_Bugbear_Dead.html", "f453fd52-7900-d5f7-101e-ce95dcb7ec9f"], "hfed6685bgcb20g4c9ag9ec0gf4677698f6f1": ["*The corpse does not stir. It will answer no more questions.*", "NARRATOR", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Forest\\FOR_Bugbear_Bugbear_Dead.html", "73cf0c85-9fdd-2e79-74c1-547b8cdcf1e2"], "h9a91f1eag925cg4639gb5ccg25b26bcc4748": ["*The corpse regards you lifelessly.*", "NARRATOR", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Forest\\FOR_Bugbear_Bugbear_Dead.html", "fd9c5bf5-e495-efc4-27f4-99b5f18a78c6"], "h8be28e4ag11e4g4c64gbb84gc86618291669": ["Who are you?", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Forest\\FOR_Bugbear_Bugbear_Dead.html", "8487af13-e7c8-6943-4098-23d7fd9894b5"], "h353d40b6ge098g4342g9c61gfc2262358039": ["Name... Grukkoh...", "b6c6764f-ba9d-4109-8b4e-c0d1da72be7d", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Forest\\FOR_Bugbear_Bugbear_Dead.html", "a14ff8a8-921d-046c-4647-0b691efe90cf"], "h597e6979g5becg44e7g89b7gc89463d9c9ca": ["What happened to you?", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Forest\\FOR_Bugbear_Bugbear_Dead.html", "a92fa63b-5d41-0bd0-6de0-e734e117d845"], "h1f34de2cg829bg4008gb8d7g81e9fcca88d2": ["Intruders... me and... Butters... ruined.", "b6c6764f-ba9d-4109-8b4e-c0d1da72be7d", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Forest\\FOR_Bugbear_Bugbear_Dead.html", "184ddaa1-1420-31cb-8fde-60aba0f1b235"], "h63eb231cg1e2cg4f46gb6edge2ebc754b022": ["Were you alone when you died?", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Forest\\FOR_Bugbear_Bugbear_Dead.html", "8ac07bf9-b546-9b29-7db7-9bbf863899ca"], "h526b1f6dg81c8g418bg9713g1f2e541833d6": ["Butters... Buthir... love...", "b6c6764f-ba9d-4109-8b4e-c0d1da72be7d", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Forest\\FOR_Bugbear_Bugbear_Dead.html", "cc3655b2-e219-e9cb-f349-00397f83de0c"], "ha6c65a3egc937g49bagac14g882c4304d535": ["Who killed you?", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".